(96, 14, 1, '', '2014-09-26 12:24:17', 144, 4532, '9e15e1fa3bd436438c991f57cf3d56571d432dae', '{"id":"14","asset_id":"102","title":"\\"Plataforma Astroinform\\u00e1tica para la Administraci\\u00f3n y An\\u00e1lisis Inteligente de Datos a Gran Escala\\"","alias":"plataforma-astroinformatica-para-la-administracion-y-analisis-inteligente-de-datos-a-gran-escala","introtext":"<p><span style=\\"font-size: 10pt;\\"><em><span style=\\"line-height: 15.3999996185303px;\\">July 30, 2014<\\/span><\\/em><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 18pt;\\">Workshop August 2014 Program Workshop 2014 Avances y desaf\\u00edos del proyecto FONDEF D11I1060<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><img style=\\"margin-right: 20px; float: left;\\" src=\\"images\\/news\\/workshop_august_2014-200px.jpg\\" alt=\\"workshop august 2014-200px\\" \\/>El Observatorio Virtual Chileno (ChiVO) es uno de los proyectos actualmente en curso en el mundo que busca contener los datos astron\\u00f3micos en sistema transparente, permitiendo que la informaci\\u00f3n est\\u00e9 a disposici\\u00f3n de todos los investigadores, independiente de su afiliaci\\u00f3n o el acceso a instalaciones de observaci\\u00f3n Con el objetivo de construir una red de trabajo consolidada y llevar a cabo una labor coordinada con las instituciones participantes en este proyecto, se realizar\\u00e1 el segundo Workshop denominado como \\"Avances y desaf\\u00edos del Proyecto FONDEF D11I1060\\u201d. Esta actividad se desarrolla en el marco del proyecto \\u201cPlataforma astroinform\\u00e1tica para la Administraci\\u00f3n y An\\u00e1lisis Inteligente de Datos a gran Escala\\u201d, el cual busca administrar y analizar los cerca de 250 terabytes de datos anuales que generar\\u00e1 ALMA, y es organizado por la Universidad T\\u00e9cnica Federico Santa Mar\\u00eda, Pontificia Universidad Cat\\u00f3lica de Chile, Universidad de Chile, Universidad de Santiago, y Universidad de Concepci\\u00f3n, junto al Observatorio Atacama Large Millimeter\\/submillimeter Array (ALMA) y Red Universitaria Nacional (REUNA).<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">El workshop presentar\\u00e1 el trabajo desarrollado por las siguientes instituciones: Universidad T\\u00e9cnica Federico Santa Mar\\u00eda, Pontificia Universidad Cat\\u00f3lica de Chile, Universidad de Chile, Universidad de Santiago y Universidad de Concepci\\u00f3n, donde estas expondr\\u00e1n sus avances con respecto sus respectivas investigaciones y contribuciones al proyecto. Siendo esta una instancia de retroalimentaci\\u00f3n entre estas organizaciones participantes. As\\u00ed como tambi\\u00e9n se generar\\u00e1 la oportunidad de dar a conocer el proyecto a la comunidad, quienes tendr\\u00e1n la posibilidad de conocer en m\\u00e1s detalle el proyecto.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">La inscripci\\u00f3n se debe realizar en el siguiente link:&nbsp;<a href=\\"https:\\/\\/docs.google.com\\/forms\\/d\\/1jn0Tqvyqz6LshfMIhhZaUFcctHb_TMVzFEBX3jwBytY\\/viewform?c=0&amp;w=1\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Workshop Registration<\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">A continuacion te presentamos el programa correspondiente al workshop del dia 1 de Agosto del 2014:<\\/p>\\r\\n<hr>","fulltext":"","state":"1","catid":"12","created":"2014-09-25 19:46:00","created_by":"144","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-09-26 12:24:17","modified_by":"144","checked_out":"0","checked_out_time":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","publish_up":"2014-09-25 19:46:00","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\"}","version":"7","ordering":5,"metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":"26","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
(97, 11, 1, '', '2014-09-26 12:24:17', 144, 2468, 'b38252db817f8779b03dc0cc12e23c4524d22c41', '{"id":"11","asset_id":"91","title":"New ALMA Equipment Designed in Chile","alias":"new-alma-equipment-designed-in-chile","introtext":"<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">New equipment for transporting one of the most sensitive components of the ALMA array \\u2014 the antennas Front End (cryogenic refrigerators) \\u2014 has been delivered to ALMA by the National Radio Astronomy Observatory (NRAO), the North American associate of the Atacama Large Millimeter\\/submillimeter Array. This new vehicle, which will save lots of time and increase safety during maneuvers, was completely designed and built in Chile. It is the first shipment of one of four vehicles for handling the Front Ends that hold the set of detectors inside ALMA\\u00b4s antennas, and is part of the technological exchange policy with the host country.<br \\/><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/almaobservatory.org\\/en\\/press-room\\/announcements-events\\/746-new-alma-equipment-designed-in-chile\\">READ THE FULL STORY<\\/a><br \\/><br \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<hr \\/>","fulltext":"","state":"1","catid":"12","created":"2014-09-22 17:21:52","created_by":"144","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-09-26 12:24:17","modified_by":"144","checked_out":"0","checked_out_time":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","publish_up":"2014-09-22 17:21:52","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\"}","version":"4","ordering":4,"metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":"11","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0);
